result.name: Saizeriya Italian Restaurant

reviews.text: Great food at a cheap price. Fast service for a quick meal. Pizzas, pastas, soups, salads, garlic breads, chicken wings, bottomless cup of soda (all you can drink) licensed too for a glass of white/red wine $16hk as well as sold by the bottles and beer too. Great place for the family, young or old.
They do not speak Italian. The food is just like all who knows to do it their way can do it. But the fair is far fair then others who cook, prepare and serve like most. Affordable.

Affordable prices. Food quality just OK. Not an authentic Italian restaurant. It's more like canteen food. The chicken spinach was by far the most delicious out of the three dishes ordered though the chicken was a bit dry. The spaghetti was not al dente. It's on the soft side. There were just two mussels on the dish and overcooked.
Good taste，reasonable n kind service.
The cost performance is pretty high here.

result.name: 薩莉亞意式餐廳

reviews.text:
物超所值的義式餐廳
義粉，披薩及雞翼，牛排，沙拉，飲品，全部都ok
就算各點一份，都係港幣200樓下，真心推介！

Great food at a cheap price. Fast service for a quick meal. Pizzas, pastas, soups, salads, garlic breads, chicken wings, bottomless cup of soda (all you can drink) licensed too for a glass of white/red wine $16hk as well as sold by the bottles and beer too. Great place for the family, young or old.
人手可能不足，碟同杯有污渍，食物跟其餘分店一樣好味！

便宜，等30分鐘以上。最大問題是極極極極吵，職員大力執拾餐具、大聲叫入座號碼、大聲叫桌號埋單，在唔大聲對方聽唔到之下，顧客更大聲談話。惡性循環下，整間餐廳吵得要命，我帶住耳機，才能吃完。之後去ikea食熱狗。零星！

Cheap, but noisy. Need to wait more than 30 minutes. Staffs shouted out numbers, customers talked loudly. I wore my headsets in order to finish my meal. I went to IKEA for a hot dog afterwards.
